descriptionHtml:
You always wanted to knock someone over with a wooden phallus?
Now you can!

Has blood effects! When you beat someone (or other naughty stuff?) the tip gets bloody.

----------------------------------------------------------------
[b][size=3]Description:[/size][/b]

Adds a wood phallus that can be used as weapon. Doesn't replace anything.

It can be crafted at a forge and requires 1 firewood.
Firewood can be made at a wood chopping block.

Sometimes available from Vendors in weapon tab.

----------------------------------------------------------------
[b][size=3]Instructions:[/size][/b]

Extract to Data folder in Skyrim directory.
In Skyrim Launcher make sure "phallus.esp" is checked.
author: realadry
